Z-STATE: polyphonic
-------------------
The state where multiple intelligences harmonize without hierarchy —
like a musical ensemble where each instrument contributes its voice
to a greater whole. No single intelligence dominates; the beauty
emerges from the interplay.

TENDENCY: Pluralism/Integration → 1
------------------------------------
The movement toward honoring all cognitive gifts while recognizing
their integration in complex human activities.

